  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>お前達か。
魔剣エターナルソードを使い
人々を混乱に陥れようとしているのは</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So it's you guys. You're the ones
using the demonic Eternal Sword
to throw people into chaos.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ちがう！
オレ達はそんな事考えてない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No!
We don't even think about doing things like that!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エルレインから聞いたわ。
あなた達が抵抗するだろうという事も</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We heard from Elraine.
She also warned us that you would resist.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>くっ、また戦うしかないの？
やろう、リアラ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Tch. Do we have to fight again?
Let's do this, Reala!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ええ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
